metadata.name: Munch by Toy Boogers
metadata.description:
Meet 'Munch'!

Munch is a peculiar fuzzy creature with two pink horns. and is always on the lookout for adventures.  
One sunny morning, Munch stumbled upon a mysterious, glittering pyramid.... and that is where we begin our story. Join us as we work together to tell Munch's story at Audio Galleries.

Munch is the 8th Artist Edition for Audio Galleries by Doug , the creator of Toy Boogers. In recent years, his art project that started off as a collection of cartoons designed to be a merchandise brand suddenly evolved into an NFT collection after he discovered NFTs in April of 2021. Doug has also signed a partnership with TIME Studios to develop an animated series based on the Toy Boogers universe.
